# ─── Script environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# All database configuration (credentials, port, container name, image) is
# read directly from the mode-specific env file at runtime:
#
#   compose mode    →  ../compose/.env
#   standalone mode →  ../standalone/.env
#
# This file exists so Bun does not complain about a missing .env, and to let
# you add any script-level overrides that are NOT related to the database
# (e.g. CI flags, logging verbosity, ...).
#
# Example:
#   LOG_LEVEL=debug
